vaulthalla (0.33.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  - Implemented setup and teardown commands in shell protocols.
  - Added certbot support for nginx setup with domain options.
  - Added remote PostgreSQL setup command with configuration options.
  - Adopted a low-prompt install policy, removing routine debconf prompts.
  - Updated post-installation scripts to conditionally handle PostgreSQL bootstrap and nginx integration.
  - Added cached draft support to changelog generation.
  - Added CLI support for Debian changelog updates, including distribution and urgency options.
  - Documented the transition from prompt-based installation to CLI-driven orchestration.

 -- Cooper Larson <cooper@valkyrianlabs.com>  Tue, 21 Apr 2026 22:38:22 +0000
